======
OpenMP
======

example1: Threaded "hello, world" code and how to use the cluster.
example2: Some pitfalls: cache-thrashing, false-sharing and mutex pain.
example3: Work-sharing loops - the OpenMP mainstay.
example4: Some examples - e.g. matrix multiplication.
example5: Task parallel programming with OpenMP, using the 'sections' directive.
example6: Debugging examples and GDB cheat-sheet.
